<topic id='attribute_reason_for_out_of_area_referral_for_adult_acute_mental_health.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: REASON FOR OUT OF AREA REFERRAL FOR ADULT ACUTE MENTAL HEALTH - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The reason why a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>
 has received a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_referral_request">REFERRAL REQUEST</xref>, for a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
with assessed acute mental health needs requiring adult mental health admitted 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 care and                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
who is resident outside of the referring 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>'s usual local network of 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
For further information, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>
 part of the gov.uk website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/oaps-in-mental-health-services-for-adults-in-acute-inpatient-care"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Guidance on Out of Area Placements</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
</body>
